Yeremia o loiboni oji Hanania


1   Ore ake teilo ari, te nkiterunoto e nkitoria e Sedekia olaiguanani le Yuda, to lapa le imiet lo lari liong'uan naairorie nanu Hanania olayioni le Asuri, ilo oiboni oing'uaa Gibeon, tiatua enkaji o Laitoriani, te dukuya ilapolosak o ltung'ana pooki, ejo, 
2  “Nji ejo Olaitoriani loo lororani, Enkai e Israel: Atigila nanu ina shata e murt o laiguanani le Babilon. 
3  Ore te rishata oo larin oare naa kashuku nanu ayau ene wueji nena masaa pooki e nkaji o Laitoriani, apa naatanapa Nebukadnesa olaiguanani le Babilon aitung'uaa ene wueji neya Babilon. 
4  Kayau sii ashuku ene wueji Yekonia olayioni le Yehoiakim, olaiguanani le Yuda, o lelo yararot pooki ooing'uaa Yuda apa ooshomo Babilon, Olaitoriani ojo, amu kagil nanu enchata e murt o laiguanani le Babilon.”


5  Neitoki oloiboni le Nkai oji Yeremia airorie Hanania ilo oiboni te dukuya ilapolosak o ltung'ana pooki apa ooitashe tiatua enkaji o Laitoriani; 
6  nejo oloiboni le Nkai oji Yeremia, “Esai! Metaasa Olaitoriani neijia; meitobira Olaitoriani lelo rorei limbonuo iyie metisipata, neshuku ayau ene wueji aitung'uaa Babilon nena masaa e nkaji o Laitoriani, o lelo yararot pooki. 
7  Ore eyia toning'o taata ele rorei lairo nanu ining'ito iyie nening'ito iltung'aa pooki. 
8  Ore apa iloibonok ooiturukutuo te dukuya iyie o nanu ebaiki apa neibonutuo olarrabal, o lameyu o lmeitai tialo nkuapi kumok o nkitoriak kituaak. 
9  Ore oloiboni oibonu eseriani, ore ake pee ebaya ororei leilo oiboni, neyioulouni taa aajo esipa Olaitoriani oiriwua ilo oiboni.”


10  Neya ilo oiboni oji Hanania nena keek naatii emurt e Yeremia ilo oiboni le Nkai, negil ninche, 
11  neiro Hanania te dukuya iltung'ana pooki, ejo, “Nji ejo Olaitoriani, kaiko nanu neijia agil enchata e murt e Nebukadnesa olaiguanani le Babilon aitayu te murt oo nkuapi pooki te rishata oo larin oare.” Kake eshomo Yeremia oloiboni le Nkai enkoitoi enye.


12  Ore te nkiti rishata eidipa oloiboni Hanania atigila nkeek aitayu te murt e Yeremia ilo oiboni le Nkai, nelotu ororei lo Laitoriani enetii Yeremia ejo: 
13  “Shomo, tiaaki Hanania, nji ejo Olaitoriani: itigila iyie nkeek, kake akaitobir nanu te rishata enye isekenke. 
14  Amu nji ejo Olaitoriani loo lororani, Enkai e Israel: Atipika nanu shumata emurt e kuna kuapi pooki esekenkei e sinkaisho te Nebukadnesa olaiguanani le Babilon, naa keisiaai ninche ninye, amu aishoo nanu ninye ebaiki ing'uesi e ong'ata.” 
15  Nejoki Yeremia ilo oiboni le Nkai ilo oiboni oji Hanania, “Toning'o Hanania: eitu iyie kirriu Olaitoriani ninchoo iyie kulo tung'ana meisiliga elejare. 
16  Neaku nji ejo Olaitoriani: ‘Ng'ura, kaaiwuang'ie nanu iyie ti oriong e nkop. Ore tele ari ake niye iyie, enkaraki niroro inenkiser tialo Olaitoriani.’ ”


17  Ore teilo ari ake, to lapa li opishana, neye oloiboni oji Hanania.

